msgstr ""
"安装前，您需要确保固件/驱动和 CANN 已正确安装，更多详情请参考 "
"[昇腾环境搭建指南](https://ascend.github.io/docs/sources/ascend/quick_install.html)。"

#: ../../source/installation.md:29
msgid "Configure hardware environment"
msgstr "配置硬件环境"

